<paragraph id="BB2791ED1C3C06CFDAB79A55DCE66679" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="D462DE2343794FBAF09138FA3AA82B1B" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="BF5A806B027315556A6453D9550D5C9A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Taxonomy</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
This species was described as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="C462984C095B3FD6BCAB0C2BFA2BF5A7" genus="E." lsidName="E. (C.) caucasicus" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="caucasicus" subGenus="C.">E. (C.) caucasicus</taxonomicName>
based on larvae collected in the Alborz Mts. (
<bibRefCitation id="A2B1E48D06EC4610571EFB8800F4C432" author="Braasch, D" journalOrPublisher="Reichenbachia" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="261 - 272" refId="B12" refString="Braasch, D, Soldan, T, 1979. Neue Heptageniidae aus Asien (Ephemeroptera). Reichenbachia 17: 261 - 272" title="Neue Heptageniidae aus Asien (Ephemeroptera)." volume="17" year="1979">
Braasch and 
<normalizedToken id="CDB7B5F841CE7BCEE83407A465E08F14" originalValue="Soldán">Soldan</normalizedToken>
1979
</bibRefCitation>
). Elevated to species level by 
<bibRefCitation id="BC5FF58C0545FF61BB5777071DC8F49A" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ympev.2020.106735" author="Hrivniak, Ľ" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B22" refString="Hrivniak, Ľ, Sroka, P, Bojkova, J, Godunko, RJ, Soldan, T, Staniczek, AH, 2020b. The impact of Miocene orogeny for the diversification of Caucasian Epeorus (Caucasiron) mayflies (Ephemeroptera: Heptageniidae). Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution 146: 106735. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ympev.2020.106735" title="The impact of Miocene orogeny for the diversification of Caucasian Epeorus (Caucasiron) mayflies (Ephemeroptera: Heptageniidae). Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution 146: 106735." url="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ympev.2020.106735" year="2020 b">Hrivniak et al. (2020b)</bibRefCitation>
