<taxonomicName id="4542F9EB5C784DB90EE3EDF4C0761AC5" authority="" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeorus (Caucasiron)" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Caucasiron">Epeorus (Caucasiron)</taxonomicName>
species. The holotype probably lost. Paratypes are currently deposited in SMNS and Biology Centre of the Czech Academy of Sciences, Institute of Entomology, 
<normalizedToken id="52BD515B3F606FC0494AB29E8742B8F2" originalValue="České">Ceske</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="8AF85457E5660DA688A154E1C7FE479B" originalValue="Budějovice">Budejovice</normalizedToken>
, Czech Republic (IECA). Imagines and subimagines not described.
</paragraph>
